  "content": {
    "problemStatement": "Given an array that is sorted and then rotated around an unknown point. Find if the array has a pair with a given sum 'k'.\n\nNote: It may be assumed that all elements in the array are distinct.\n\nExample:\n\nInput: arr[]={11,15,6,8,9,10},k=16\n\nOutput: yes\n\nThere is a pair (6,10)with sum 16",
    "constraints": [
      "1 <= N <= 10^3"
    ],
    "inputFormat": "The input has the size and elements of the array.\n\nThe last row has the sum value.",
    "outputFormat": "Print Yes/No",
